    "lyrics": {
      "text": "When the bod-----i-less one was__ se--cret-ly__ com-mand-------ed,__ in haste he came_____ and stood be--fore___ Jo--seph’s dwell-------ing,__ and spake un----to the Maid------en___ who__ knew not__ wed----lock: The One_____ who hath__ bowed__ the Heav----ens__ by His des---cent____ is held_____ and con--tained__ un-chang----ing___ whol----ly in___ thee._____ See--ing Him___ tak-ing on the form__ of a ser--vant_____ in thy__ womb,____ I stand__ in__ awe and cry__ to____ thee:__ Re-joice,____ thou pure__ and un-wed---ded____ Bride."
    }
